author: gordonsmith
msg: Removed the 'sdk' directory inside of flex/falcon/trunk, which had a zipped-up Apache Flex SDK and a bunch of SWC files.
Now Falcon builds its SDK by copying files from flex/sdk/branches/develop. It assumes that you have done an 'ant main' there.
